resources.string: Since 1951 officially known as Botanical Garden Rombergpark, Rombergpark was basis for Romberg\'s Castle Park. The beginnings, however, reach back to the year 1818 when the family of Romberg erected a park around their property in Dortmund-Bruenninghausen. Since 1926 it is property of the city of Dortmund and is used as a botanical garden since then.
